data.description: Great home in the city but feels like the country. Nestled in the woods across from Sentara Medical Center you will find this nice 3 bedroom, 3 bath home with lots of updates. Large living room with gas logs, large dining area in kitchen.  Sunroom is large but not heated or cooled. Attached 2 car carport with storage and detached carport with storage. One demand hot water system one yr old. Roof 2016.  In the city with city water and utilities but still hooked up to septic. This home is close to everything.
